default 
defaultIn Israel and the OPTs, the younger generation is less inclined to support negotiations towards a real peaceful r
defaultesolution
default, since they 
defaulthave come of age during four wars (the Second Intifada, the Second Lebanon War, Operation 'Cast Lead' and the recent Operation 'Pillar of 
defaultDefence
